♪ <i>I wanna get a rise</i> ♪

439
00:33:24,004 --> 00:33:26,217
♪ <i>Oh, rise</i> ♪

440
00:33:27,762 --> 00:33:29,974
♪ <i>Oh, rise</i> ♪

441
00:33:31,393 --> 00:33:33,690
♪ <i>I wanna get a rise</i> ♪

442
00:33:39,076 --> 00:33:41,455
♪ <i>Oh, rise</i> ♪

443
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,046
♪ <i>Yeah, rise</i> ♪

444
00:33:46,173 --> 00:33:49,137
♪ <i>I wanna get a rise</i> ♪

445
00:33:49,806 --> 00:33:51,601
[audience cheering, applauding]

446
00:35:07,210 --> 00:35:08,212
So…

447
00:35:10,049 --> 00:35:11,845
Why didn't you call me?

448
00:35:12,470 --> 00:35:13,765
I was too busy.

449
00:35:14,559 --> 00:35:17,313
It's always, "I'm too busy, I'm too busy."

450
00:35:19,276 --> 00:35:21,113
I finally made time.

451
00:35:26,290 --> 00:35:27,752
Well,

452
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,089
why don't you answer a riddle?

453
00:35:33,930 --> 00:35:38,648
It's free for you, but precious to me.

454
00:35:39,567 --> 00:35:40,569
And

455
00:35:41,738 --> 00:35:43,909
it's something only I can give,

456
00:35:44,952 --> 00:35:47,625
and something only you can break.

457
00:35:49,377 --> 00:35:50,463
What is it?

458
00:35:53,385 --> 00:35:54,387
I wonder.

459
00:35:59,439 --> 00:36:01,151
My heart.

460
00:36:45,031 --> 00:36:47,578
[person] <i>Did you see the tattoo, Masahiro?</i>

461
00:36:48,495 --> 00:36:49,624
A little.

462
00:36:50,584 --> 00:36:52,003
It's like I said, right?

463
00:36:55,259 --> 00:36:57,096
You'll do it, right?

464
00:37:01,313 --> 00:37:03,108
Is the money really there?

465
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:31,289
Can you take me back to Tokyo?

466
00:37:31,916 --> 00:37:33,043
[driver] Yes.

467
00:37:33,753 --> 00:37:35,172
I've changed my mind.

468
00:37:36,509 --> 00:37:38,303
[phone ringing]

469
00:37:42,270 --> 00:37:43,439
[phone beeps, stops]

470
00:37:46,111 --> 00:37:47,196
Father.

471
00:37:47,948 --> 00:37:50,704
It seems Saho will agree to the divorce.

472
00:37:51,664 --> 00:37:55,630
<i>You have ruined everything.</i>

473
00:37:56,131 --> 00:37:59,053
<i>That is why I cleaned it up.</i>

474
00:37:59,972 --> 00:38:02,226
Father, you can't.

475
00:38:03,312 --> 00:38:06,944
Let me take care of it. I can do it alone.

476
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:11,077
<i>I will have a good talk with Saho.</i>

477
00:38:11,662 --> 00:38:15,211
Take a long, hard look at yourself.

478
00:38:16,798 --> 00:38:17,925
Please…

479
00:38:19,385 --> 00:38:21,223
let me handle it.

480
00:38:21,306 --> 00:38:22,893
<i>It is already done.</i>

481
00:38:24,229 --> 00:38:27,485
<i>Saho will go back to her parents
after the divorce.</i>

482
00:38:28,571 --> 00:38:32,913
<i>And you will stay away from that mistress.</i>

483
00:38:34,792 --> 00:38:38,090
I know everything.

484
00:38:40,762 --> 00:38:42,724
I will not accept

485
00:38:43,893 --> 00:38:46,899
any more lies from my oldest son.

486
00:38:47,526 --> 00:38:49,237
[crying, sniffling]

487
00:38:51,324 --> 00:38:52,703
I will do well.

488
00:38:55,542 --> 00:38:56,961
I will

489
00:38:58,130 --> 00:39:00,050
be a son you can be proud of.

490
00:39:01,888 --> 00:39:03,850
You can't.

491
00:39:06,396 --> 00:39:07,524
You are too weak.

492
00:39:24,098 --> 00:39:27,063
And? What should I do?

493
00:39:31,404 --> 00:39:34,202
Do you love Ichiro?

494
00:39:37,208 --> 00:39:38,252
Probably.

495
00:39:45,725 --> 00:39:48,230
Then, do this.

496
00:39:52,990 --> 00:39:56,998
<i>Send a message to Ichiro.</i>

497
00:39:59,252 --> 00:40:01,297
<i>A sweet message.</i>

498
00:40:03,260 --> 00:40:06,308
<i>Tell him you're worried about his wife.</i>

499
00:40:08,270 --> 00:40:11,067
<i>It will be a perfect scenario.</i>

500
00:40:12,069 --> 00:40:15,660
<i>Just like the one you've dreamed of.</i>

501
00:40:17,706 --> 00:40:22,507
<i>Then ask if you can see him.</i>

502
00:40:24,052 --> 00:40:26,515
<i>At his favorite place.</i>

503
00:40:28,728 --> 00:40:30,982
<i>Your makeup that day should look special.</i>

504
00:40:32,944 --> 00:40:37,788
<i>Be sure to make yourself look
especially beautiful and enchanting.</i>

505
00:40:43,256 --> 00:40:46,471
<i>Go early and wait for him.</i>

506
00:40:49,227 --> 00:40:52,108
<i>At a place where he can see you.</i>

507
00:40:54,696 --> 00:40:58,579
<i>When he arrives, take his hand</i>

508
00:40:59,288 --> 00:41:01,961
<i>and tell him how much you've missed him.</i>

509
00:41:06,010 --> 00:41:08,098
<i>Then say, "Let's take a walk."</i>

510
00:41:08,891 --> 00:41:12,440
<i>Talk about your memories
of when you first met.</i>

511
00:41:13,483 --> 00:41:18,368
<i>And the troubles you overcame together.</i>

512
00:41:22,126 --> 00:41:24,130
<i>Then turn around</i>

513
00:41:25,090 --> 00:41:28,556
<i>and tell him you have
something important to tell him.</i>

514
00:41:29,641 --> 00:41:34,568
<i>Say, "I pray that our relationship will
never change."</i>

515
00:41:37,741 --> 00:41:40,037
<i>And finally…</i>

516
00:41:44,588 --> 00:41:46,049
I'm pregnant.

517
00:43:12,221 --> 00:43:14,225
Translated by Annie Chen

